    "_publishedAt": "2023-10-05T09:12:06+01:00",
    "description": "Discover how ICOs harness the power of network effects to fuel their success. ICOs and network effects, a dynamic duo!",
    "thumbnail": {
      "url": "https://www.datocms-assets.com/101962/1690860184-cbc9-img1.png"
    },
    "contentBlock": [
      {
        "mainContent": {
          "value": {
